trans-unit.source: Contains a collection of static <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection"></xref> objects, which is used when the connections are declared in content pages and the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager"></xref> control is declared in a master page.
trans-unit.target: 정적의 컬렉션을 포함 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection"> </xref> 콘텐츠 페이지에서 연결이 선언 되는 때 사용 되는 개체 및 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager"> </xref> 마스터 페이지에서 컨트롤을 선언한 합니다.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: 이 클래스는 상속 될 수 없습니다.

trans-unit.source: The ProxyWebPartConnectionCollection class is used in a specific development scenario.
trans-unit.target: ProxyWebPartConnectionCollection 클래스는 특정 개발 시나리오에 사용 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: If a Web Parts application uses master pages, with the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control declared in a master page, and individual <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection> objects declared in content pages as static connections, the ProxyWebPartConnectionCollection class is used.
trans-unit.target: 웹 파트 응용 프로그램으로 마스터 페이지를 사용 하는 경우는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>마스터 페이지에서 선언 하 고 개별 컨트롤 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection>로 선언 된 개체 콘텐츠 페이지에서 정적 연결 ProxyWebPartConnectionCollection 클래스는 사용 됩니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: In the content pages, multiple <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager> controls can be declared, which differs from the ordinary rule that only one <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control can be declared on a page.
trans-unit.target: 콘텐츠 페이지에서 여러 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>컨트롤 선언 될 수 있습니다, 한 일반 규칙에서 다른 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>페이지에 컨트롤을 선언할 수 있습니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: Each <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager> control on a content page can contain a `<StaticConnections>` element, and this element can contain one or more declared `<asp:webpartconnection>` elements.
trans-unit.target: 각 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>콘텐츠 페이지의 컨트롤에 포함 될 수 있습니다는 `<StaticConnections>` 요소, 그리고이 요소는 하나 이상의 선언 포함할 수 있습니다 `<asp:webpartconnection>` 요소.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: The ProxyWebPartConnectionCollection class is used by the Web Parts control set to create a collection of all the static connections declared in each content page, and these collections are ultimately added to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A> collection in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control.
trans-unit.target: ProxyWebPartConnectionCollection 클래스는 웹 파트 컨트롤 집합 각 콘텐츠 페이지에 선언 된 모든 정적 연결의 컬렉션을 만드는 사용 되 고 이러한 컬렉션에 추가 궁극적으로 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A>컬렉션에는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>컨트롤.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A>
